@DATABASE "Crime Busters"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Crime Busters"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                               Crime Busters
                               =============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Time " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(60158,33)"}          60158,33
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(61012,201)"}          61012,201
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47219,201)"}          47219,201


                         The "Infinite Lives" and "Infinite Time" POKEs
                         were by me. The "Immunity" POKE was originally
                         printed as "Infinite Lives" in ZXAMPOKE, and 
                         the "Infinite Time" POKE went into an infinite
                         loop once you completed a level. Now it doesn't!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
